-- Botswana Plans to Sell National Telecommunications Co. Stake by End-April
-- B y   J e r r y   B u n g u
-- 2011-02-07T14:47:54Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-02-07/botswana-plans-to-sell-national-telecommunications-co-stake-by-end-april.html
  Botswana  plans to sell 49 percent of
its national telecommunications company by the end of April this
year, Finance Minister Kenneth Matambo said in a budget speech
today in the capital, Gaborone.  The government is finalizing a privatization plan for state
companies, Matambo said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Jerry Bungu in Gaborone at 
 jbungu@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
